<item>
            <title>[SOLR-15756] Contrib READMEs missing from builds</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15756</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I mentioned this on the Solr 9.0 blockers thread: &lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/rbde21ecda719611a7b0d34e25b555038a2afdbeebff76960a96ea62a%40%3Cdev.solr.apache.org%3E&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/rbde21ecda719611a7b0d34e25b555038a2afdbeebff76960a96ea62a%40%3Cdev.solr.apache.org%3E&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Builds from Jenkins are missing all the README.md files for everything in the &lt;tt&gt;contrib/&lt;/tt&gt; directory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since the .jars are stored under &lt;tt&gt;dist/&lt;/tt&gt;, that means in cases where there are not dependencies there is not any directory for some contribs at all (i.e., &lt;tt&gt;contrib/analytics&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;contrib/scripting&lt;/tt&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
